ob kept falling out. She must&#39;ve been sunbathing until late because she came in basically in a bikini and a cover.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-extends-las-vegas-residency-with-32-more-shows-3518855">Adele extends Las Vegas residency with 32 more shows</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
